Download the rpm packages:

MySQL-client-community-5.1.25-0.rhel5.i386.rpm
MySQL-server-community-5.1.25-0.rhel5.i386.rpm
MySQL-devel-community-5.1.25-0.rhel5.i386.rpm

url to download the packages:

http://mirrors.ukfast.co.uk/sites/ftp.mysql.com/Downloads/MySQL-5.1/

Start the service :

/etc/init.d/mysql start

(refer this site:https://sites.google.com/site/radienallienz/linux/howto-install-mysql-on-linux)

>mysql

